"\tgv to gsview but this does not work. You probably need gv or ghostview\n"
"\tif you insist on previewing your work as postscript. Exporting to ps\n"
"\tand later viewing it with gsview DOES work.)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/lyx.txt:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
